description: Baroness Davina Dust has brought the personal doctor of Mr. Kayne under her control. With rope and chains she restricts him into a helpless position. Now she's going to play with him. She wants him to tell her the most intimate secrets of Mr. Kayne. She torments her victim with her soiled nylons, putting them into the doctor's mouth. She gives him endless tease and denial. Completely at her mercy he has to put up with her naughtiness. But he still resists so she starts to torment him with breath control. Will intense facesitting, smothering, and more golden showers make him talk?
title: Ep 13 - Golden Shower for the Doctor: the Baroness Goes Naughty
